}}{{TIDTOC|switch}} ==Overview== "MADE IN TAIWAN" and "52-000028-00" is silkscreened on the board of one production model SS2105. :A date code of '''0134''' (Aug. 2001) is etched onto the bottom of this board.
===Probable included PSU(s)=== The power supply included with this switch (or at least some) seems to be an '''unbranded''' AD41-1200500DU.
